Colorize Vol 01 Mixed by Sebastian Weikum Extended Mixes (2014) 

                    Trance, Progressive | Colorize (Enhanced)

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 02:10:46 | 301 Mb


With over 30 releases to date on the fast rising Enhanced Music sub-label, Colorize prepares for its first feature compilation, mixed by label veteran and top Polish talent, Sebastian Weikum. The imprint which aims to release only the highest quality in colorful melodic Progressive and Deep House has put together no less than 18 sublime tracks featuring more than 10 unreleased exclusives.
